<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM3.9">
<l>aṅkai yāḻi yaraṅka ṉaṭiyiṇait</l>
<l>taṅku cintait taṉipperum pittaṉāy</l>
<l>koṅkar kōṉkula cēkaraṉ coṉṉacol</l>
<l>liṅku vallavark kētamoṉ ṟillaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no affliction here to those who master</l>
<l rend="indent">the words uttered by Kulacēkaraṉ, the king of the Koṅku people,</l>
<l rend="indent">being a unique great madman whose mind remains on the pair of feet of</l>
<l rend="indent">Raṅga with a discus in [His] beautiful hand.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
